  <brief_title>Sofosbuvir, Ledipasvir, Ribavirin for Hepatitis C Cirrhotics, Genotype 1</brief_title>
  <acronym>SL50</acronym>
  <official_title>Sustained Viral Response Rate in 50 Subjects With Cirrhosis Due to Hepatitis C, Genotype 1, Treated With 12 Weeks of Sofosbuvir, Ledipasvir and Ribavirin</official_title>
